    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes a mechanism for a link state routing protocol to coordinate the value of a routing timer parameter amongst routers in the flooding domain. The document also defines the solution to one specific case: the agreement of a common convergence timer value for use by routers in network convergence.</t>
